    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a reliable daily driver for someone who doesn't mind some cosmetic and mechanical character. The engine runs and the car is drivable, though it does have a minor oil leak and the suspension is starting to feel a bit soft. Visually, the paint has faded in several spots on the roof and trunk, and there are noticeable scuffs on the bumpers along with a small dent on the passenger door. Inside, the upholstery shows significant wear and the air conditioning takes a few minutes to get cold. It's a solid, functional car that has been used regularly but will eventually need some attention to keep it in good shape.",
